Introduction

MISAMO (a portmanteau of the names of members Mina, Sana, and Momo) is a Japanese sub-group of TWICE under JYP Entertainment and Warner Music Japan.

The unit made their official debut in Japan on July 26, 2023, with their first mini album "Masterpiece".
